videos.description: Ben Simmons shares how he thought the Sixers played well against the Cavaliers and how his conversation with Robert Covington went, who suffered an apparent lower back injury late in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Simmons pleased with 76ers' overall play) 2017/12/9

videos.headline: Simmons pleased with 76ers' overall play

videos.description: LeBron James admits that it was tough turnaround for the Cavaliers after waiting out a five-hour delay in Indiana Friday night before playing a role on the Cavs' last 22 points in a win Saturday.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (LeBron says he doesn't need to score to help team) 2017/12/9

videos.headline: LeBron says he doesn't need to score to help team

videos.description: Dwyane Wade knows that LeBron James gets the headlines, but says that Kyle Korver is a key player and expresses how proud he is of his teammates for pulling through the exhaustion after a five-hour flight delay the night before.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Wade continues to be impressed with Korver) 2017/12/9

videos.headline: Wade continues to be impressed with Korver
